node.text:
This was a 10 month progress video, and I can finally say I am proud of myself.
This is in no way shape or form saying that I used to be “fat” or “skinny”, I just did not like the condition my body was in. I didn’t feel good inside and I didn’t like how it looked on the out. I wanted to feel healthy all around and I just didn’t. 
on October 1, 2020, I wrote myself a note in my phone that said I will start today, and I haven’t stopped. Whenever I need a helper or a reminder, I just open up that note and it reminds me how far I have come. It does get hard sometimes but not nearly as hard as I thought it would be. 
This is only the beginning… ❤️
